schemeContent.detailedDescription_md:
The &amp;quot;District Central Cooperative Banks and through its Branches: For Consumer Durables T.V., Fridge and Two Wheelers Loan&amp;quot; scheme launched by the Co-operation, Food and Consumer Protection Department, Tamil Nadu, offers loans for the purchase of consumer durables, including T.V.s, refrigerators, and two-wheelers. The loan covers up to 75% of the product cost, with no upper ceiling, and is subject to a 14% interest rate (subject to change).
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;br&gt;

eligibilityCriteria.eligibilityDescription_md:
  - The beneficiary should be a resident of Tamil Nadu.
  - Loans should be applicable only for Consumer durables such as T.V., Fridge and two wheelers.

&lt;br&gt;
